metadata.name: A veteran driver with a suspended driving license
metadata.description:
Wang Jue looked directly at the towering, dark figure in front of him, indescribable, indescribable, irresistible and invincible.



"Look at me, bow to me, and become one with me at last, and you will find endless truth...... Everlasting, sink down." The whisper of the ancient god sounded in Wang Jue's head, in a soft, seductive tone.



Wang felt that he wanted to move but could not. The whispers of the old gods still lingered in his mind.
